Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早啊麻里香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么早打电话给我\N迟到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我正要搭电车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你声音很沙哑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你学分够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你还想毕业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我没空玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸出车祸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我妈养我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,学费也是硬凑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再给我麻麻添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,人生最后的暑假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我还要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想自己赚点学费
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈很辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,已经这么晚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你点名的 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,(电车广播)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.03,0:32:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 麻里香 早
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.03,0:32:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你又迟到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.05,0:32:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你又翘课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.05,0:32:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,实习课也不上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.05,0:32:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要考证了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.06,0:32:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,明年我们都要找工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.03,0:32:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一年暑假好好玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.03,0:32:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没钱找个男朋友就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.04,0:33:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一年暑假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.04,0:33:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我连交男朋友的时间都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.05,0:33:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得男生很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.05,0:33:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你遇到痴汉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.06,0:33:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真的遇到了 要勇敢的大叫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.03,0:33:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.03,0:33:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我快迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.06,0:34:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,(电车广播)
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.03,0:59:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也好累
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.04,0:59:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明天继续加油
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.04,0:59:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 妈
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.04,0:59:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉这么晚打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.04,0:59:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚下班
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.05,0:59:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正要搭电车
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.05,1:00:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.06,1:00:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己想坐的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.06,1:00:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,明年考到教师证就能正常工作了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.03,1:00:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.04,1:00:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上大学还蛮好玩的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.04,1:00:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会小心的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.05,1:00:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在四町目那边
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.05,1:00:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,走一下就到了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.06,1:00:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.06,1:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.03,1:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我会怕
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.05,1:03:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.05,1:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.05,1:26:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.04,1:27:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.05,1:28:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.05,1:39:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.03,1:39:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.05,1:41:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.06,1:46:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.05,1:47:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.04,1:48:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.05,1:49:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.06,1:49:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是大学生吧 有玩联谊吗
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.06,1:49:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,下次来我们痴汉社团玩啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.04,1:49:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,听说大学私生活都很淫乱
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.04,1:49:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有参加性交社啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.05,1:49:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的参考书好像是要考老师吗
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.05,1:49:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好想当你的学生哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.03,1:50:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,女老师吗 好萌哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.04,1:50:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,童颜的女教师好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.05,1:50:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.05,1:50:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天也搭10:40的车吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.05,1:50:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不搭这个影片会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.03,1:50:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会被散播出去
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.04,1:50:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会想逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.04,1:50:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还是想照片被传出去呢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.05,1:51:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,复制 下载 转帖
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.05,1:51:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,扩散
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.06,1:51:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.03,1:51:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,会被转帖出去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.04,1:51:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,全员到齐等你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.06,1:53:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.05,1:55:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.06,1:56:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.06,1:56:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉耽误各位乘客的时间
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.03,1:56:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,目前终点站 池波站
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.04,1:56:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,发生铁道人身事故
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.04,1:56:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,电车无法驶入车站
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.04,1:56:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再次为耽误乘客时间感到抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.05,1:56:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊  放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.06,1:56:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.04,1:58:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:51.05,1:59:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,湿答答的
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.06,2:00:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.06,2:11:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.06,2:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要住手
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.06,2:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看你这么湿
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.04,2:11:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,2:16:35.05,2:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,2:19:32.06,2:19:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍
Dialogue: 0,2:20:17.04,2:20:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,2:22:19.06,2:22:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
